                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120408-48-victim549 t18120408-48-viclabel264"></join>; I lost the property on the 2d of March, at the sign of <placeName id="t18120408-48-crimeloc265">the Crown, Hornsey-lane, Highgate-hill</placeName>
