                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120408-48-off262 t18120408-48-crimeloc265"></join>; I went into that house where there were twenty-five Irishmen, navigators. The prisoner took the breeches from my arm, they were handed from one to another; I asked the prisoner for the breeches, he said he had not got them. I afterwards went into the room with 
               <persName id="t18120408-48-person551">
                  Lewis 
                  Page
               <interp inst="t18120408-48-person551" type="surname" value="Page"></interp>
